Install WSL 2, Scoop, and Chocolatey on Windows

Install XCode Developer Tools, set default shell to ZSH,
and install Homebrew on macOS

Refer to this article for updating macOS headlessly:
    - https://thehomeofthefuture.com/how-to/update-macos-from-the-command-line/

Install APT stuff on Linux and install Gnome tweaks (multi-monitor,
shortcut for centering and moving windows)
